      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione work-area                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-ref-cod-tmo-cod      .
           move      spaces               to   w-ref-cod-tmo-trt      .
       ref-cod-tmo-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura referenza                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
