      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se campo da accettare              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rr-cli-min           =    zero
                     go to tdo-ric-sel-160.
           if        rr-cli-max           =    rr-cli-min or
                     rr-cli-max           =    zero
                     go to tdo-ric-sel-155
           else      go to tdo-ric-sel-160.
       tdo-ric-sel-155.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test                                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rr-dpz-min           =    spaces or
                     rr-dpz-max           =    spaces
