                     go to reg-ric-sel-300.
           if        rr-cli-min           =    zero
                     move  9999999        to   rr-cli-max
           else      move  rr-cli-min     to   rr-cli-max             .
       reg-ric-sel-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice dipendenza massimo                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
